Rowdy Wolf:








Rowdy Wolf's eyes went wider than before, watching Zyber's transformations. 
She was another bot. He gaped his mouth, showing off his sharp carnivorus 
teeth. He chuckled a short while, stepping back in a few steps, and held his 
chest with one hand. He still held his rifle in the other.
"You're a bot!" he said, laughing. "A bot. I thought you were a talking 
wolf." He put a hand up. "But not offense. It's rare that I've seen other 
bots. I thought this bot named Quickstrike was the only bot I would ever 
come in contact with." He paused. "From what territory did you come from?"
